hang with your friends and neighbors around the fire pit.', 'Get a work-out in at our Fully Equipped Fitness Center or recharge after a long day in our tranquil landscaped outdoor courtyard.', 'Features:', 'Luxurious Bathroom, Hardwood flooring, Stainless Steel Whirlpool Appliances, Private patios on every unit, Abundant Natural Light, Spacious walk-in closets, Large windows, Washer & Dryer in unit, Granite Countertops', 'Community Amenities:', 'Controlled access property, Extra Storage closets starting at $95 per month, Smoke-free building, Resident Website w/ Online Bill Pay, Work Orders and more, Electric car charging stations, Courtyard with massive gas fire pit, 2 Gas BBQ Grilling areas, Bicycle Garage for $20 monthly, Easy access to public transportation, Walk to Ballard Farmers Market, 24 hour fitness center with State of the art cardio studio and Strength training equipment, Spacious Clubhouse with Fireplace, Package Concierge Lockers for 24 hour access, Rooftop deck w/ views & Wi-Fi access, Fantastic Coffee Machine w/ espresso, hot cocoa and more!,', 'WalkScore = 92, Reserved, garage parking space for $160 monthly', 'Pet Policy', 'KOI treats your pets are a part of the family, with complimentary MudBay treats at the office every day!', '-2 pet maximum per apartment home', '-Pet deposit of $300', '-Pet Rent of $50 per pet', "Restricted Breeds: Pit Bull Terriers/Staffordshire Terriers, Rottweiler's, Doberman Pinschers, Chows, Presa Canarios, Akitas, Alaskan Malamutes, Wolf-Hybrids", 'Please contact our leasing professionals for more information.', 'Income Requirements:', "Applicant's gross income must be 3 times the monthly rent.", 'Guarantors accepted!', 'Must have 5x the monthly rent as income and good credit.', 'Use this link for more info:', '<URL>', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', '06rfHf2J']
